\cf0 \cb2 David Manthey - Robert W. Baird & Co. Incorporated, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Christopher Snyder - Morgan Stanley, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Jacob Levinson - Melius Research LLC\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Ryan Merkel - William Blair & Company L.L.C., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Stephen Volkmann - Jefferies LLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Christopher Glynn - Oppenheimer & Co. Inc., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Kenneth Newman - KeyBanc Capital Markets Inc., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Sabrina Abrams - BofA Securities, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Neal Burk - UBS Investment Bank, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Deane Dray - RBC Capital Markets, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Nigel Coe - Wolfe Research, LLC\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Thomas Moll - Stephens Inc., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Guy Drummond Hardwick - Barclays Bank PLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Patrick Baumann - JPMorgan Chase & Co, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Christopher Dankert - Loop Capital Markets LLC, Research Division\cb1 \
